<span id="freeTextContainer10346851469814365766">Leora Cika Waldman loves puppies, flowers, rain, coffee and beautiful china cups. But most of all she adores her handsome husband, Kevin, who is her best friend ever.She writes because she is thrilled to witness, through the lives of her characters, how people succeed in face of difficulties and how human character is shaped accordingly. </span>

