      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/23458389-nirupa-and-the-book-of-shadows">Quotes from Nirupa and the Bo...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
